  "title": "Field Integer Power",
  "root": "",
  "statement": "Let $F$ be a field. For $a\\in F$, powers $a^n$ with $n\\in\\mathbb{W}$ are\ndefined recursively. If $a\\ne0$ and $n\\in\\mathbb{Z}$ is negative, define\n\\[\na^n:=(a^{-1})^{-n}.\n\\]",
